ibased company has already shed some of the smaller brands it says collectively contribute little to its operating profit but that has hurt sales which have declined over the past three years and the companys share price shares of pg are up less than  percent this year rival johnson  johnsons stock is up  percent in the same period colgatepalmolive co is up  percent and kimberlyclark corp is up  percent business channel trian said that its not looking to break up pg replace taylor or remove other board members pg said in a statement that its maintained an active dialogue with trian but that its sticking with its current strategy trian hasnt provided any new or actionable ideas that will help create more shareholder value it said analyst kevin grundy of jeffries said in a client note that while pg has taken sensible steps to boost shareholder value and theres no guarantee that peltz will get a seat on pgs board the perceived value of his presence may lead to greaterfaster realization of cost savings andor raise the execution bar at pg text news to  for alerts feds accused sa drug dealer involved in yearolds death lawyers for sa man set to die thursday appeal to us    catch every san antonio area moment click to like mysa on facebook the latest cartel members hand blown off in military fight near texas rising star takes racy photo backstage in sa longtime texas rodeo announcer dies at  bakery chain adds another sa location man crossing  states on horseback to achieve texas dream photos k reno transforms sstyle sa condo sa woman accused of posting revenge porn after break up mom speaks out as en photo of transgender son goes viral  sa brands named finalists in heb contest graphic video shows moment ohio ride breaks apart throws riders lawyers for san antonio man set to die appeal to us supreme celebowned music food complex weeks away from opening readers favorite restaurants bars in sa underrated restaurants that sa foodies crave photos rb star khalid stuns downtown sa